 ORDBMS :-  
 ------------------

  => Object Relational DBMS
  =>  It is the combination of RDBMS & OOPS

                ORDBMS  =  RDBMS + OOPS (reusability)

  => rdbms doesn't support reusability but ordbms supports reusability
 
